                <h1 style="font-size:16px; padding-top: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px;">Eight Things No One Ever Teaches You About Grilling</h1>





				<p class="subhead" style="font-size:14px;font-style:normal;">TV's grilling expert offers barbecue techniques for how long to grill, how much to grill, and pretty much everything else you need to know for perfect meat this summer<br /><br /><i><b>PLUS:</b> <a href="http://www.esquire.com/features/recipes-for-men/barbeque-tips/easy-grilling-recipes-0509" alt="easy grilling recipes">Easy grilling recipes</a>, the <a href="http://www.esquire.com/features/recipes-for-men/barbeque-tips/best-summer-drinks-0509" alt="best summer drinks">best summer drinks</a>, tips on <a href="http://www.esquire.com/features/cooking-perfect-steak" alt="cooking perfect steak">cooking steak</a>, and more from <a href="http://www.esquire.com/features/recipes-for-men/barbeque-tips/backyard-barbecue-tips-0509" alt="barbecue tips">Esquire's backyard</a>!</i></p>


				
